txt.en: 'I am glad you were there, for the Red Sky Clan may not have survived that assault!'

'In an effort to extend a hand to those in Mordor who do not rally under a banner of shadow, we will lend aid to those in need. You have spent time with the Red Sky Clan in Agarnaith, have you not?

'They are continually in confrontation with the forces of Seregost. We must be vigilant for the Red Sky Clan are now one of our greatest allies in Gorgoroth.

'Would you go to their village and assure them of our continued watch?'

<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest has a one hour time limit. The timer will begin upon accepting the quest. This quest can be completed with one or two adventurers.</rgb>
'We must protect the Red Sky Clan at any cost.'

The Red Sky Clan of Bhol Rûdh is up against impossible odds in their conflict with the forces of Seregost.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest has a one hour time limit. The timer will begin upon accepting the quest.</rgb>
You should return to Candúr and apprise him of your efforts.
